In [4]:
densenet = DenseNet121(
    include_top=False,
    input_shape=(224,224,3)
)
for layer in densenet.layers:
        layer.trainable = True

shape_input_2 = (IMAGE_HEIGHT,IMAGE_WIDTH,1)
model_chex = Sequential()
model_chex.add(Conv2D(3,kernel_size=(1,1),activation='relu',input_shape=shape_input_2))
model_chex.add(BatchNormalization())
model_chex.add(densenet)
model_chex.add(BatchNormalization())
model_chex.add(Conv2D(16,kernel_size=(4,4),activation='relu'))
model_chex.add(BatchNormalization())
model_chex.add(Conv2D(8,kernel_size=(3,3),activation='relu'))
model_chex.add(BatchNormalization())
model_chex.add(Conv2D(4,kernel_size=(2,2),name='coords'))
model_chex.add(Flatten())

sgd_optimizer = tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=0.01)

model_chex.compile(optimizer=sgd_optimizer, loss='mean_absolute_error', metrics='accuracy')
model_chex.summary()

In [0]:
early_stopping_monitor = EarlyStopping(
    monitor='val_loss',
    min_delta=0,
    patience=20,
    verbose=1,
    mode='auto',
    baseline=None,
    restore_best_weights=True
)
model_check=ModelCheckpoint(
    filepath='/content/drive/My Drive/Colab Notebooks/Capstone Project/model_chex_1_checkpoint',
    monitor='val_accuracy',
    mode='max',
    save_best_only=True
    )
LR_on_plteau = ReduceLROnPlateau(
    monitor='val_loss', factor=0.1, patience=3, verbose=1, mode='auto')

history_chex=model_chex.fit(X_train,y_train,
          validation_data=(X_val,y_val),
          callbacks=[early_stopping_monitor,model_check,LR_on_plteau],
          epochs=50,
          batch_size=75)

#plotting the bounding boxes and images for the patients selected above
style.use('ggplot')
num_of_img = 20 #number of images u want to plot
start_index = 20
fig, axs = plt.subplots(math.ceil(num_of_img/4),4,figsize=(100,100))

j=0
for i in np.arange(start_index,start_index + num_of_img):
  plt.subplot(math.ceil(num_of_img/4),4,j+1) #create subplot
  fig=plt.imshow(X_test_plot[i], cmap=plt.cm.bone)
  
  bb = patches.Rectangle((y_test[i][0], y_test[i][1]),
                                     y_test[i][2], y_test[i][3],
                                     linewidth = 6,
                                     edgecolor = 'r',
                                     facecolor = 'none')
  fig.axes.add_patch(bb)
  bb2 = patches.Rectangle((y_pred_chex[i][0], y_pred_chex[i][1]),
                                     y_pred_chex[i][2], y_pred_chex[i][3],
                                     linewidth = 6,
                                     edgecolor = 'b',
                                     facecolor = 'none')
  fig.axes.add_patch(bb2)
  j=j+1
plt.show()
